00:23:16.960 --> 00:23:18.560
Then let’s do this.

00:23:19.320 --> 00:23:23.040
When you’re with Grandma, you have to try to be strong.

00:23:23.560 --> 00:23:30.440
But when you’re with me,
you can be yourself and cry as much as you want to.

00:23:31.160 --> 00:23:33.040
I’ll be a shoulder for you to lean on.

00:24:00.280 --> 00:24:01.440
I’m sorry…

00:24:03.280 --> 00:24:04.760
